hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有假定的剖面
$$\frac{u}{U_e}=\sin\!\Bigl(\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\Bigr)\,,\quad 0\le y\le\delta.$$
1. 位移厚度：
$$\delta^*=\int_0^\delta\Bigl(1-\sin\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\Bigr)dy
=\delta-\frac{2\delta}{\pi}
=\delta\Bigl(1-\frac{2}{\pi}\Bigr)\,. $$
2. 动量厚度：
$$\theta
=\int_0^\delta\sin\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\Bigl(1-\sin\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\Bigr)dy
=\int_0^\delta\sin\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\,dy
-\int_0^\delta\sin^2\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\,dy.$$
计算每一项：
$$\int_0^\delta\sin\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\,dy
=\frac{2\delta}{\pi},\quad
\int_0^\delta\sin^2\frac{\pi y}{2\delta}\,dy
=\frac{\delta}{2}.$$
因此
$$\theta
=\frac{2\delta}{\pi}-\frac{\delta}{2}
=\delta\Bigl(\frac{2}{\pi}-\frac12\Bigr)
=\delta\,\frac{4-\pi}{2\pi}\,. $$
3. 形状因子：
$$H=\frac{\delta^*}{\theta}
=\frac{\bigl(1-\tfrac{2}{\pi}\bigr)\delta}
{\tfrac{4-\pi}{2\pi}\,\delta}
=\frac{2(\pi-2)}{4-\pi}\,. $$
4. 壁面切应力和表面摩擦：
$$\tau_w=\mu\Bigl(\frac{\partial u}{\partial y}\Bigr)_{y=0}
=\mu U_e\frac{\pi}{2\delta},\quad
c_f=\frac{\tau_w}{\tfrac12\rho U_e^2}
=\frac{\pi\,\nu}{\delta\,U_e}.$$
5. 使用
$$\frac{c_f}{2}=\frac{C_1}{Re_\theta}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\frac{\pi\,\nu}{2\delta\,U_e}
=\frac{C_1}{U_e\theta/\nu}
\;\Rightarrow\;
C_1=\frac{\pi\,\theta}{2\delta}
=\frac{4-\pi}{4}\,. $$
6. 因此
$$C_1\,H
=\frac{4-\pi}{4}\;\frac{2(\pi-2)}{4-\pi}
=\frac{\pi-2}{2}\,. $$
